   patient chronicity and medication status. One study examined chronically
   ill, unmedicated patients (Kerr and Neale 1993); a second study included
   chronically ill, medicated patients (Mueser et al. 1996); and a third
   study examined acutely ill, medicated patients (Bellack, Blanchard and
